<div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;" trbidi="on"><div class="post-header"><div class="post-header-line-1"></div></div><div class="post-body entry-content" id="post-body-4318723312877360969" itemprop="articleBody"><div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;" trbidi="on">Hello Everyone,</div><div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;" trbidi="on">To enable a DFF in a Self-Service page using the personalization, please do the following steps:</div><div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;" trbidi="on"><br />1: Go to Personalize Page at the top of the page.<br />2: Then click (Expand All)&nbsp;then click&nbsp;(Complete View)<br />3: Search for&nbsp;the name of the&nbsp;DFF you want to enable it (for example:&nbsp;Additional Absence Details)<br />4: Click personalize&nbsp;pen and then set&nbsp;Rendered to True.<br />5: Click Apply and you may need to restart the Apache server.</div><div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;" trbidi="on"></div><div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;" trbidi="on">BR,</div></div></div>